channel.title: 614 coding help
channel.description: Hello, I am new to rsps's in general and am using a 317. But do to the fact of the bad GFX of many things, some bugs and glitches, not able to add custom models, and the overall the performance of it, I have decided to move on to a 614. Yes I know its a huge jump, but before you start flaming or trolling, I am simply asking if someone can please point me in the right direction as to learning how to code a 614 or even post a tut or a few helpful words of wisdom ;). thank you in advance, Brandon
